title: People in LA are FAKE… ft. Gabriel Zamora
description:
This week on Fool Coverage, Manny and Laura invite the one and only Gabriel Zamora! They talk about his brow implants, dating as an influencer, how he started in the beauty community, GAY RIGHTS, adjusting to LA culture, his new podcast Blunt Talk Podcast (rebranding soon), and much more!
Follow Gabriel in IG: @gabrielzamora
Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
